{"word":"G3708 - ὁράω - horáō - hor-ah'-o - Behold","slug":"G3708","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὁράω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>horáō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>hor-ah'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Behold"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BF;&#x0314;&#x03C1;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - horao&#x0304;</b> - <i>hor-ah'-o</i><p/>Properly to <i>stare</i> at (compare <a href=\"#/G3700\">G3700</a>), that is, (by implication) to <i>discern</i> clearly (physically or mentally); by extension to <i>attend</i> to; by Hebraism to <i>experience</i>; passively to <i>appear:</i> - behold, perceive, see, take heed."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2300\">G2300</a>, <a href=\"#/G2334\">G2334</a>, <a href=\"#/G2529\">G2529</a>, <a href=\"#/G3705\">G3705</a>, <a href=\"#/G3706\">G3706</a>, <a href=\"#/G3707\">G3707</a>, <a href=\"#/G4308\">G4308</a>, <a href=\"#/G517\">G517</a>"}]}